<h2>
	In-Memory Lenses
</h2>
<p>
	Powered
 by Fractal Cache™ technology, Platfora automatically transforms massive
 datasets into highly responsive lenses. The high-performance query 
engine makes access to big data fast and scales-out to terabytes of 
in-memory data. Lenses are refined and updated based on the needs of the
 end-user.
