<h2>
	Hadoop Data Refinery
</h2>
<p>
	Platfora
 transforms Apache Hadoop into a work engine. Adaptive Job Synthesis™ 
synthesizes specialized MapReduce jobs that automatically extract 
detail, perform calculations and downstream analysis, building lenses 
efficiently and on demand. All datasets in Hadoop are cataloged and can 
be securely browsed by any Platfora user.
</p>